    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT389-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ kuṟṟēvaṉmakaṉāṉmai (C2: -makaṉāl) varaivu malinta tōḻi
                    talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered to HER by the confidante, who rejoiced,
                    with HIS servant, about the marriage. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT389">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> neykaṉi kuṟumpūḻ kāya māka</l>
                    <l> vārputam peṟuka tōḻi yattai</l>
                    <l> peruṅka ṉāṭaṉ varainteṉa vavaṉetir</l>
                    <l> naṉṟō makaṉē yeṉṟaṉe</l>
                    <l> ṉaṉṟē pōlu meṉṟurait tōṉē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l rend="indent"> Of curry [and] small quail, melting in ghee,</l>
                    <l> he may obtain [his] fill, friend!</l>
                    <l rend="indent2"> Since the man from the land of big stones is chosen ,</l>
                    <l> I said to him “is [that] good, son?”</l>
                    <l> “It seems good”, he told [me]. </l>


                </lg>
            </div>
        </body>
